Maintainer: Retl
Site: https://github.com/retl/BloonsPlusPlus/

Based upon: Bones++, Bones
Original Authors: diginc, Jonathan Drain
Original Sites: https://github.com/diginc/BonesPlusPlus/ http://www.d20source.com/roleplaying-tools/dicebot
Language: Ruby 1.8

Description: It's part me playing around to get a a grounding in ruby, and partly me adding text-based digital toys to the dicebot for use on #FalloutEquestria channel on the Canternet IRC channel when our usual Bones process goes down.
